# Shared by core-api/Dockerfile and core-api/tools/CoreApi.Migrator/Dockerfile.
# `tools/` used to be excluded here; that broke the migrator build because
# its Dockerfile lives under tools/ and copies the directory in. The main
# core-api image only COPYs `src/`, so leaving tools/ in the build context
# doesn't grow it.
**/bin/
**/obj/
*.md
.env*
